{"tid":377943,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩！原來<大會堂演奏廳>係李克勤自己寫！","createTime":"2017-08-28T06:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T00:56:48.000Z","uid":49388,"like":359,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0ecf16e78227ef250b48c6062be303b1990090","tid":377943,"uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:02:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Tp5WMzqxyps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTp5WMzqxyps&d=cc5Vyip4F%2BDnLp4ljgfpG5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ec64fa42\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Tp5WMzqxyps</a><br />\n<br />\n大會堂演奏廳<br />\n<br />\n作詞：李克勤<br />\n作曲：林慕德<br />\n編曲：林慕德<br />\n<br />\n瀟瀟颼颼悄悄夜靜無人　伴我行是寂寥<br />\n絲絲點點細雨串串落下　迷離撲朔飄渺<br />\n冰冰冷冷滴著微微柔黃　是霧燈的苦笑<br />\n飄飄涼風輕吻浪潮<br />\n<br />\n偏偏想起那次幸運回頭　大會堂裡邂逅<br />\n卿卿我我說笑靜靜垂頭　兩手輕輕緊扣<br />\n分分秒秒像是停留停留　浪漫中的演奏<br />\n可惜時光不會逗留　轉眼飄走<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=cc5Vyip4F%2BDnLp4ljgfpG5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0490db06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n<br />\n可笑是我沒法沒法不想<br />\n跟你同渡甜蜜甜蜜片段<br />\n星雨下你在笑著我<br />\n像個小丑　台下彈奏<br />\n不再害怕害怕害怕分手<br />\n分手以後無奈如舊<br />\n人漸消瘦　相愛是這樣會令我<br />\n疲倦不休　無力挽留<br />\nRepeat all once<br />\n<br />\n1988 年作品<br />\n&quot;瀟瀟颼颼悄悄夜靜無人　伴我行是寂寥&quot;<br />\n得個廿歲份詞已經寫得咁湊美<br />\n<br />\n咁睇蜂蝗gem拍埋去都唔係話好勁者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a2f70c7a4029a47a22c67f0b0e43e3a25e1041","tid":377943,"uid":49388,"like":148,"dislike":2,"score":146,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:09:25.000Z","msg":"送禮有人理<br />\n唱歌冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f16c278e312ad15b43ed0317b7f97e8e8a770c","tid":377943,"uid":49388,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:10:26.000Z","msg":"Btw 港樂既現場水平真係有今生無來世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\