if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要自己作曲<br />\n1987年早大會堂演奏廳一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n命運符號<br />\n<br />\n作詞：李克勤<br />\n作曲：李克勤<br />\n編曲：杜自持<br />\n<br />\n泥土種子　從小開始　泥裡聽著故事<br />\n無知的幼苗漸漸地懂得意思<br />\n陽光　年月裡扶持<br />\n<br />\n微雨　陪伴作衝刺<br />\n溫室中竟不知　險惡日子<br />\n<br />\n*　從前知心　已經不禁　人各散有著距離<br />\n旁邊　每個人偏偏只愛自己<br />\n漫漫　長路更迷離<br />\n難再　逃避去演戲<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=cc5Vyip4F%2BDnLp4ljgfpG5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0490db06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n不知應不應該　相信運氣<br />\n讓　讓我攀高峰帶著自豪<br />\n跌　誰沒有跌過染著糞土<br />\n但　何懼那遠處滿是圈套<br />\n隨著那勸告　憑著那線佈<br />\n來讓我看到　我碰到　我上到　到達最高 *<br />\n<br />\n#　今天到老　我像那跌不到　我想做<br />\n做我命運符號　用我力鋪我路途<br />\n只盼我有日會在星夜裡<br />\n那天我會　含淚說聲　我做到 #<br />\nRepeat * # #"},{"pid":"531bd91fe8192a878133b118f691243436f86435","tid":377943,"uid":29167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T08:21:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宋禮勤好似係華仁讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但ce 中文拎D渣wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，CE 背就有C啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e434b3a1caec21647d256264be7184d88cbbf522","tid":377943,"uid":41076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T08:30:52.000Z","msg":"嗰陣林慕德都勁<br />\n不過後來寫埋d 「呀呀A」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲奶埋共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb296d9414e7f7e800954fd4ddf9e2d5ae3cc9d","tid":377943,"uid":20654,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T08:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>宋禮勤好似係華仁讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class